Edward PITARD,<br>
Appreciate your thoughts, we all can't be as smart of BIG Ed. He stutters that's why he posted the above note twice. But, to tell you the truth, Edward Mustang Two by Fours wasn't too smart before Nam. <br>
He was so poor he didn't know the iCe cream truck carried Ice cream,he just though the nice guy came around everyday to play the music for him. <br>
He joined the service to save on postage, because they told him Vietnam was the land of no postage stamps (you wrote free on the envelope and Uncle Sam delievered them free statesides). He thought his coat of many colors were a fashion statement, never knew they were patches. <br>
That's why he joined the special forces because he wanted all those shiny buttons and medals. His recruiter told him they were made of real silver and gold. <br><br>
He voted for Johnson, cause he believed it was the same guy that made Johnson &amp; Johnson the baby powder, which he used on account of his holy underware, which he never changed. When they made him change them in the service, he cried all night. He went out and buried them that night, today the place is a toxic waste dump site.<br>
Took the Army three weeks to explain to him what toilet tissue was used for.<br>
When he found out food came in cans he used his chopper's blades to open them. <br>
He collected pop tops caused he believed they were sacred. Still carries a can opener around his neck for good luck. <br>
His first shoes were combat boots. <br>
First time through the mess hall he saved his ice cream bars in his pockets so he could eat later. <br>
When a Vietnamese invited him over for rice cakes he brought a candle. But we loved him anyways, kept coming back to the combat zones cause he liked all the pretty fireworks the enemy shot into the air for him to enjoy. We never told him any difference. <br><br>
Joe <br>
Thanks for the stats, where do you find out all this stuff, you and Batmen, he has all those little gadgets, he plays around with. <br>
M24 wants to know where Batmen bought his cape and leotards, so he can get a set, he says for Holloween, but I think he just likes the feel of silk. Claims its a PTSD disorder on account he spent some time with Naval personal off some ship in Nam. But I don't believe him. <br><br>

